Package: FitAge
Title: Functional (Fitness) Age Calculator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Filipa", "Santos Rodrigues", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "filipacsrodrigues@gmail.com")
Description: Estimates a person's functional ("fitness") age from physical
    performance measures - grip strength, sit-to-stand / sit-and-rise,
    one-leg balance, sit-and-reach flexibility, push-ups, waist-to-height
    ratio and reaction time - using the Klemera-Doubal Method (KDM). Each
    measure is calibrated against chronological age independently, so markers
    sourced from different normative datasets (NHANES, plus published norms)
    can be combined in a single model without requiring all measures on the
    same individuals.
